PrecisRe-appointment of ERROL W.A. TOWNSHEND, of Scarborough, Ontario, FLORA LIEBICH, of Toronto, Ontario, and HARRIET WOLMAN, of Toronto, Ontario, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of two years, effective November 22, 1995.
